Having a Break in Alberobello.
•
•
The Unusual N.2
Have you ever been in Alberobello? It's one of the best suggestive place in Italy in Puglia. Here a worker while he was taking a break under the "trullo", a traditional Apulian dry stone.
•
Why "UNUSUAL " series?
This is what I love the most when I visited a place: seeing what locals do during the ordinary day time. 
One of the most place shot in Ig but with a different point of view.

The Unusual: #1 Florence.
•
•
Good afternoon Instagramers!!
After more than a month I'm back! •
During this time period I didn't stop to shoot the different landscapes that I discovered.
So, I decided to start this year to tell stories about my adventure but with an unusual point of view.👀
Instagram is full of beautiful landscape. Is there anything we're missing or we are putting aside some place?🕵🏻‍♀️
